{"tid":1414675,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實斬樹封馬路有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:17:39.000Z","uid":121634,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d1b7d5c0ecc44bf894911691ceacd8541229b4","tid":1414675,"uid":121634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得上年山竹搞到成路樹，打工仔們根本返唔到工，但係奴性又迫使香港人爬都要爬番工。<br />\n你話如果呢場天災可以人為重演一次，比各位打工仔再選擇一次，唔知大家又會唔會死都要死返工呢？<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n- 樹重難搬走<br />\n- 一顆樹都夠長封哂成條路<br />\n- 多區有冧樹報告，食環同路政要用長時間處理<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 非專業人士斬樹有高機率受傷<br />\n- 一般平民工具斬成日顆樹都可能未冧<br />\n- 冧樹擊中行經車輛/途人就大0鍋<br />\n- 一顆樹種好多年，冧左好可惜<br />\n<br />\n缺點其實仲有好多，請三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53919e093262bde3c522757a9fab6774a0f29e7d","tid":1414675,"uid":121634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:43:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ca4d3803495b23dc52efdd8257d9f5ce6d6e90a9","tid":1414675,"uid":36923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"846186f6bc5bf56a65ce1a4bb68c220ab1b4dc00","tid":1414675,"uid":239606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"自然環境唔好破壞.. 要好多時間修復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f578a5d2d3f4802cce52bfcf4b10f41caaf4fba1","tid":1414675,"uid":18170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"沙田有人做<br />\n不過D樹好細棵，係種喺馬路同馬路中間嗰啲"},{"pid":"8d0e6748acc387215b98c9607f539a9e85897184","tid":1414675,"uid":247554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"到時林鄭記招 黃錦星終於有機會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1a1d580f8ef0feb3e4551aa51ee02cbb7f5110","tid":1414675,"ui